\f1\b0 \
This project aims to demonstrate how logistic regression, a simple yet powerful machine learning algorithm, can be employed for churn prediction in the telecom industry. By accurately identifying customers at risk of churn, the telecom company can take proactive measures to retain valuable customers, reduce churn rates, and enhance overall business profitability and customer satisfaction.\
